              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "3-LI-6",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.96
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The target was prepared by",
                "evaporating lithium metal enriched to 96% Li6 onto a",
                "thin copper foil. The thickness of the material and",
                "of the copper backing were measured by magnetically",
                "analyzing the elastically scattered protons at a",
                "bombarding energy of 2 Mev. At this bombarding energy",
                "the copper foil 60+-3 keV thick and the 6LiOH",
                "6.2+-0.2 keV thick."
              ]
            }
          ],
